text.tspan: Array of NFLOAT byte Floats (cf Record3) with NPROP elements,
where NPROP = (NCOL * NROW). Array is C order
ncol, nrow, xori, yori, xinc, yinc,
yflip is either 1 or -1. The value 1 for both means that
(given rotation 0) lower left cell corner is (0, 0) and is forming
a left-handed system if Z (depth) is assumed positive down,
Rotation is derived from X axis, and is positive in anti-clock direction.
inline and xline are givens as 2 numbers: [start, step] e.g. [34, 4]
